<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.6.9">
<l>teṉṉilaṅkai maṉṉaṉ cirantōḷ tuṇiceytu</l>
<l>miṉṉilaṅku pūṇvi pīṭaṇa nampik</l>
<l>keṉṉilaṅku nāmat taḷavu maraceṉṟa</l>
<l>miṉṉilaṅ kāraṟkōr kōlkoṇṭuvā</l>
<l rend="indent">vēṅkaṭa vāṇarkkōr kōlkoṇṭuvā.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Bring a staff for the one with the necklace</l>
<l rend="indent">that shines [like] lightning,</l>
<l>who, having cut to pieces the head and arms</l>
<l rend="indent">of the king of Laṅkā in the South,</l>
<l>said to lord Vibhīṣaṇa with jewels that shine like lightning</l>
<l rend="indent">“[Reign] such that my shining name reaches [the whole] kingdom.”</l>
<l>Bring a staff for the resident of Vēṅkaṭam.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
